long_description: italian pack middle east is the story of an adventure begin in dubai in 2023, carrying on the philosophy of " placing the customer at the center", that has always characterized italian pack spa since 1988.located in dubai, it's italian pack's first branches in the world, that promises itself to respond promptly, efficiently and professionally to the needs of its clients in its area of expertise, through the help of a dedicated commercial facility and a technical service on the spot. the range of packaging machines varies from simple table top ones to the most complex packaging systems for various food sectors such as: ready meals, meat, poultry, fish, seafood and desserts, in the most advanced packaging technologies. satisfying the clients' needs and exceeding his own expectations, by continuing to improve ourselves, are the guidelines that led italian pack to undertake this new adventure.
